          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-3xl text-center">
            More On Starting A Conversation About Racism....
          </h3>
          <p class="my-4">These are additional books I found helpful:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-4">
            <li>
              <Link
                href="https://www.amazon.com/You-Want-Talk-About-Race/dp/1580058825/ref=sr_1_3?crid=2MIZ0LQN9QVWF&dchild=1&keywords=so+you+want+to+talk+about+race+ijeoma&qid=1598566103&s=books&sprefix=So+you+%2Caps%2C189&sr=1-3"
                ><em>So You Want to Talk About Race</em>
