            </li>
            <li>
              <Link
                href="https://www.amazon.com/Opposite-Hate-Field-Repairing-Humanity/dp/1616209399/ref=sr_1_2?crid=3OKXYHPKZP9FO&dchild=1&keywords=the+opposite+of+hate&qid=1598566183&s=books&sprefix=The+opposite+of+hate%2Cstripbooks%2C162&sr=1-2"
                ><em
                  >The Opposite of Hate: A Field Guide to Repairing Our
                  Humanity,</em
                >
              </Link> by Sally Kohn — on how to create a neutral space for conversations
